FBIS4-36181 "drnes109_j_94034" FBIS-NES-94-109 Daily Report 6 Jun 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Aden Radio Reports Claims of Northern POW's Aden Radio Reports Claims of Northern POW's EA0606191494 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in English 1600 GMT 6 Jun 94 EA0606191494 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in English 1600 GMT 6 Jun 94 English BFN [Text] Several of the war prisoners from the northern forces who were captured in Wadi Hadhramaut reported that they had been pushed into the lost war. They said that they surrendered after their commander had run away from the battle and left them without water. They also said they are from the central territories. They expressed happiness for the brotherly reception by the forces of the DRY [Democratic Republic of Yemen] after they had surrendered.
